Visit platform: openai.com
Open Dashboard
Open API keys
Click on Create new secret key
Give any name then click on create
Copy the key 

#Invoke OpenAI APIs with python
Open terminal and type: pip install openai
Then type: pip freeze> requirements.txt
Create a new folder: hello_world
Create a main.py file
Create .env file
And write this in that file:
Code: OPENAI_API_KEY="Paste the copied key here"

